p;</p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The EXP API will not support:</p>
<ul>
<li>Searching</li>
<li>Pagination</li>
<li>Sorting</li>
<li>Caching</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Not supported for November. These fields will=
 be available in the EXP API Scheme for future use.<br><br>
 The EXP API will return up to 5000 records in 1 request, and will be store=
d in memory in the UI and will use OOTB agGrid functionality.</p><p><br></p=
><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">The payments are <strong>retrieve=
d in reverse chronological order</strong> by default</span></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
