nts requiring authorisation and scheduled payments).</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">I=
nteracting with the brand new pagination/sorting/filtering/caching CAP API<=
/span></span></li>
</ul>
